productReviews.reviewText: My velociraptor loves to play with it.
I tried to shatter it but got potato all over it.
The box this comes in is 5 yard by 6 centimeter and weights 18 gram!!
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
This green works considerably well. It mildly improves my basketball by a lot.
